data.description: Price Improvement!! Seller is motivated.Discover the perfect blend of rural charm and modern comfort with this inviting mobile home, now available for sale. Nestled on a sprawling 1.25-acre parcel of agriculturally-zoned land, this property offers a unique opportunity for those seeking a serene country lifestyle. Boasting three generously-sized bedrooms and two well-appointed bathrooms, this residence provides ample space for a growing family or those in search of additional room for hobbies and guests. The open floor plan creates a seamless flow from the living area to the well-equipped kitchen, making it an ideal space for entertaining or simply enjoying the peaceful surroundings. With room to roam on the expansive acreage and the convenience of a modern mobile home, this property promises a tranquil and spacious living experience. Furthermore, the generous acreage makes it a great place for farm animals, making it an ideal home for those looking to embrace the joys of rural life. Don't miss the chance to make this your country retreat.
